Package de.feu.massim22.group3.agents

Class BdiAgentV2

java.lang.Object
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.Agent
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.BdiAgent<IDesire>
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.BdiAgentV2
All Implemented Interfaces:
Supervisable
public class BdiAgentV2 extends BdiAgent<IDesire> implements Supervisable
The class BdiAgentV2 defines an agent implementation of group 3 in the massim agent contest 2022. The class is one variant out of two implementations of the group. The other implementation is BdiAgentV1. Please be aware, that BdiAgentV2 is no successor of BdiAgentV1. Both implementations define a separate approach and are not connected to each other.
Author:
Melinda Betz
